attributes.review: This app is very poorly designed imo. Every time I click to a new page it asks me to get notifications, so I have to constantly click out of pop-ups that the app gives me. That’s complete garbage, should just ask once and not bother me again.That makes it very hard to navigate the app smoothly and find what I’m looking for. From a computer scientist’s perspective, that’s unnecessary and will push users away from engaging it. I promise you, this app is not worth your time.
